update_eq_of_ne:
theorem update_eq_of_ne {m : nat} {a : α} {v : nat → α} (k : nat) : k ≠ m → update m a v k = v k :=
  by
  intro h1
  unfold update
  rw [if_neg h1]
#align update_eq_of_ne update_eq_of_ne
update_eq:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `omega.update -/
theorem update_eq (m : nat) (a : α) (v : nat → α) : (omega.update v m a) m = a := by simp only [update, if_pos rfl]
#align update_eq update_eq
pred_mono_2':
theorem pred_mono_2' {c : Prop → Prop → Prop} {a1 a2 b1 b2 : Prop} : (a1 ↔ a2) → (b1 ↔ b2) → (c a1 b1 ↔ c a2 b2) :=
  fun h1 h2 => by rw [h1, h2]
#align pred_mono_2' pred_mono_2'
pred_mono_2:
theorem pred_mono_2 {p : α → β → Prop} {a1 a2 : α} {b1 b2 : β} : a1 = a2 → b1 = b2 → (p a1 b1 ↔ p a2 b2) := fun h1 h2 =>
  by rw [h1, h2]
#align pred_mono_2 pred_mono_2
